@AgentClaret

Maybe if you actually read, you wouldn't make yourself look like an idiot. The FULL UNLOCK is referring to all the extra addons and bonus gear you get when you pre-order. Normally, players would have to unlock those things as they progress in the game. 

This game gives you all the fully unlockable pre-order weapons, bonuses, etc.

@deathtrooper30
What's you're point? Most games don't get cracked till the release date or maybe a day before at the most.  There are very talented crackers out there that know how EA and origin protect their product with encryption.  Just because one game was cracked early doesn't mean another game will, they might even increase the security because of the breach in previous games.  

I say if you're downloading it for free and not buying it you have no right to bitch about how long it takes to crack.
